      "text": "рҹҸ—пёҸ INFRASTRUCTURE: Kubernetes (K8s) + Terraform (IaC) + Docker + GitHub Actions (CI/CD)\nAgent workers as K8s deployments | Auto-scaling on queue depth | Blue-green deploys | Secrets via Vault/SOPS",
