    {
      "id": "legend",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 1320,
      "width": 1300,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "вҳ… = End-to-End Owner Agent (owns outcomes, not just tasks)  |  All agents connect to Event Bus (pub/sub) + Context Store (PostgreSQL)\nData flow: Trigger вҶ’ Orchestrator вҶ’ Queue вҶ’ Agent Worker вҶ’ LLM Gateway вҶ’ MCP Tools вҶ’ Context Store вҶ’ Event Bus вҶ’ Next Agent\nHuman gates: Architecture вңӢ | Production deploys вңӢ | Model promotion вңӢ | Legal docs вңӢ | Pricing вңӢ | Customer comms вңӢ",
